{
    "slug": "10-propositos-literarios-de-ano-nuevo",
    "title": "10 propósitos literarios de Año Nuevo (que probablemente no cumplas)",
    "excerpt": "Leer por placer, abandonar libros sin culpa, no fingir que entendiste ese libro... Una lista de buenos propósitos lectores que seguro romperás antes de febrero.",
    "content": "<div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-orange-50 p-6 border border-amber-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-amber-500 text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg\">1</span><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Leer por placer, no por culpa</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">No todo tiene que ser importante, profundo o \"necesario\".</p></div></div></div><div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-50 to-pink-50 p-6 border border-rose-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-rose-500 text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg\">2</span><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Abandonar libros sin pedir perdón</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">Si no pasa nada, no pasa nada.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-50 to-purple-50 p-6 border border-violet-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-violet-500 text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg\">3</span><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Terminar los libros que realmente quiero terminar</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">No los que debería.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 border border-blue-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-500 text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg\">4</span><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">No fingir que entendí ese libro</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">Decir \"no me gustó\" también es una lectura válida.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50 to-cyan-50 p-6 border border-teal-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-teal-500 text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg\">5</span><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Leer sin mirar Goodreads antes</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">Ni estrellas, ni hype, ni peleas en los comentarios.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-green-50 p-6 border border-emerald-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg\">6</span><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">No comprar libros solo porque \"algún día\"</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">(O mentirme mejor cuando lo haga).</p></div></div></div><div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-50 to-amber-50 p-6 border border-yellow-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-yellow-500 text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg\">7</span><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Devolver los libros prestados</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">O asumir que ahora forman parte de mi biblioteca.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-red-50 p-6 border border-orange-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-orange-500 text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg\">8</span><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Leer algún clásico</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">Por algo no caducan.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-50 to-rose-50 p-6 border border-pink-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-pink-500 text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg\">9</span><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">No subrayar todo</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">Subrayar menos.<br/><span class=\"text-sm italic\">(Subrayar igual).</span></p></div></div></div><div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-violet-50 p-6 border border-indigo-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg\">10</span><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Recordar por qué empecé a leer</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">Porque era divertido. Porque acompañaba. Porque sí.</p></div></div></div></div>",
